Signal index survives in 0.85·N ≥ 0.5·N chains (coherent). Noise index (entity-specific, p=4k/D=1/64) survives θN with prob (1/64)^(N/2) → ~10⁻⁶ at N=7. **Exponential noise crushing, not √N.**

